---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import DocsSidebar from '../../components/DocsSidebar.astro';
---

<Layout title="FAQ | GemCrest Docs">
    <!-- Documentation Layout -->
    <div class="docs-layout">
        <DocsSidebar currentPath="/docs/faq" />

        <main class="docs-content">
            <h1>Frequently Asked <span class="accent">Questions</span></h1>
            <p>Find answers to common questions about GemCrest.</p>

            <h2>Licensing</h2>

            <h3>What is included in the lifetime license?</h3>
            <p>Your ₹5,000 license includes:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Full access to all GemCrest features</li>
                <li>Lifetime updates (minor versions, e.g., 1.x)</li>
                <li>Email support</li>
                <li>Offline pincode database for India</li>
                <li>Custom invoice templates</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Can I use GemCrest on multiple computers?</h3>
            <p>Each license is valid for one device. If you need to use GemCrest on multiple computers, please contact
                us for multi-device licensing options.</p>

            <h3>What happens if I change my computer?</h3>
            <p>Contact us at <a href="mailto:aravcrestlabs@proton.me"
                    style="color:var(--rose-gold);">aravcrestlabs@proton.me</a> with your license code and we'll help
                you transfer the license to your new device.</p>

            <h3>I lost my license code. What should I do?</h3>
            <p>Email us from the same email address you used for purchase. We'll verify and resend your license code.
            </p>

            <h2>Technical</h2>

            <h3>Does GemCrest require internet?</h3>
            <p>No! GemCrest works 100% offline. Internet is only needed for:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>One-time license activation</li>
                <li>Downloading updates (optional)</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Where is my data stored?</h3>
            <p>All your data is stored locally on your computer in an encrypted database. We never have access to your
                business data.</p>

            <h3>How do I backup my data?</h3>
            <p>Go to <strong>Settings → Backup</strong> and click "Create Backup". Save the backup file to a USB drive
                or external storage for safekeeping.</p>

            <h3>GemCrest won't start. What should I do?</h3>
            <ol>
                <li>Try restarting your computer</li>
                <li>Run GemCrest as Administrator</li>
                <li>Check if antivirus is blocking the app</li>
                <li>Contact support with error details</li>
            </ol>

            <h3>Can I run GemCrest on Mac or Linux?</h3>
            <p>Currently, GemCrest is only available for Windows 10 and later. Mac and Linux versions may be considered
                in the future based on demand.</p>

            <h2>Features</h2>

            <h3>Does GemCrest support GST billing?</h3>
            <p>Yes! GemCrest generates fully GST-compliant invoices with proper tax calculations (currently 3% GST on
                jewelry). Your GSTIN appears on all invoices.</p>

            <h3>Can I track old gold exchanges?</h3>
            <p>Absolutely. The invoice screen has a dedicated "Exchange Items" section where you can add old jewelry
                received from customers. The exchange value is automatically deducted from the total.</p>

            <h3>Does it support different gold purities?</h3>
            <p>Yes. GemCrest supports 24K, 22K, 18K, 14K, and custom purities. Rates are automatically calculated based
                on your 24K gold price.</p>

            <h3>Can I email invoices to customers?</h3>
            <p>Yes. After creating an invoice, you can export it as PDF and email it directly to customers.</p>

            <h2>Payment & Refunds</h2>

            <h3>What payment methods do you accept?</h3>
            <p>We accept all major payment methods through Razorpay:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Credit/Debit Cards</li>
                <li>UPI (GPay, PhonePe, Paytm)</li>
                <li>Net Banking</li>
                <li>Wallets</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Do you offer refunds?</h3>
            <p>Due to the nature of digital products, all sales are final. Please review our documentation and features
                carefully before purchasing. See our full <a href="/legal/refund-policy"
                    style="color:var(--rose-gold);">Refund Policy</a>.</p>

            <h3>Is GST included in the price?</h3>
            <p>Yes, the ₹5,000 price is inclusive of all taxes.</p>

            <h2>Still Have Questions?</h2>
            <p>If you can't find the answer you're looking for, please <a href="/contact"
                    style="color:var(--rose-gold);">contact us</a>. We typically respond within 24 hours.</p>
        </main>
    </div>
</Layout>
